                    <li>Resolution: 32x32～1280x1024</li>
                    <li>Aspect ratio: 1:3～3:1</li>
                    <li>Framerate: 40 fps or below</li>
                    <li>Bitrate: 3 Mbps or below (1 M = 1024 K)</li>
					<li>Closed GOP, Square pixel ratio, Progressive scan</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                Audio: AAC-LC
                <ul>
                    <li>Channel: mono or stereo</li>
                    <li>Bitrate: 320 Kbps or below</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Recommended settings</h3>
